## Google Reviews (Maps JavaScript API + Places)
## 1) Create an API key in Google Cloud
## 2) Enable "Maps JavaScript API" (and Places)
## 3) Restrict the key by HTTP referrer for your domain
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=

## Your Google Place ID (for Café Keppler)
VITE_GOOGLE_PLACE_ID=

## Resend (Sollicitatieformulier)
## RESEND_FROM must be a verified sender in Resend (or use onboarding@resend.dev for testing)
RESEND_API_KEY=
RESEND_FROM=Café Keppler <onboarding@resend.dev>
RESEND_TO=kitzmann24@outlook.com


